<Defs>
  
 <!--■■■■■■■■■■■■■■■■■
     BEING A JERK
  1. Bio-Asset Deconstructed (Pawn) aka "ButcheredHumanlikeCorpse"
  2. Bio-Asset Deconstructed (Colony) aka "KnowButcheredHumanlikeCorpse"
  3. Biomaterial Extracted (Guest) aka "KnowGuestOrganHarvested'
  4. Biomaterial Extracted (Colonist) aka "KnowColonistOrganHarvested"
